::Prowl::

Prowl felt the orbs tingling again as his mind lashed out once more. 
The grenade slowed down, and a laser shot hit it, sending it flying 
off and exploding in the air. He looks at Iron Raptor.

-Are you allright, love?- he 'asks' as he walks toward her. It was 
strange how in several minutes they had gone from speach to thought.

(Some people had Qs about Prowl's telikinetic ability, and he will 
not be able to bend or bounce shots with his mind, or missiles. Just 
thrown objects or loosely controlled ones, like a grenade, rock, 
dagger, etc...)
